      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Mint-condition used car that presents beautifully inside and out. It starts, runs, and drives exactly as it should, with a very clean interior, excellent exterior finish, and no meaningful signs of wear. A buyer can expect a genuinely well-kept, like-new example that needs nothing beyond routine ownership.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
