      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "Fair condition overall. Shows visible cosmetic wear and age, and it may need some maintenance or repairs to keep it running reliably. Still a practical option for a buyer looking for a usable vehicle at a more affordable price.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, honest transportation with plenty of life left for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical, budget-friendly option for commuting, first-time drivers, or anyone needing dependable wheels without a big upfront cost. A smart value purchase for someone who appreciates straightforward ownership and real-world utility.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Great opportunity for someone handy or looking for an affordable project. This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option with plenty of usable life and a lot to offer for the right buyer. If you want dependable transportation at a down-to-earth price or something you can tinker with and make your own, this one is worth a look. Priced fairly and ready to go to its next owner.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with strong project potential. Starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with a powertrain that feels fundamentally solid and a chassis that still has usable life left in it. Not a showpiece, but a straightforward platform for someone who wants affordable transportation, a weekend fixer, or a budget build. Presents with cosmetic wear and age-related flaws consistent with use, but the core mechanical package makes it worth a look. If you know how to turn a wrench, this is the kind of car that can be sharpened up without breaking the bank.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Rough around the edges, but it gets the job done. Cheap, honest, and priced to move fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom-perfect\u2014instead, it offers honest, hard-earned character and the sort of charm that makes a practical daily, weekend fixer-upper, or budget-friendly backup with real personality. If you appreciate a vehicle with presence, potential, and a price that leaves room to make it your own, this one deserves a look. A solid opportunity for someone who sees value beyond the surface.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for anyone looking for simple, affordable transportation. It shows age and use, but it remains a solid option for a value-focused buyer who wants a straightforward car at an accessible price point. A sensible choice for commuting, first-time drivers, or anyone seeking inexpensive mobility.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next owner. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s an affordable way into motoring for someone handy or anyone after a cheap runaround/project. There\u2019s plenty of life and usefulness here for the right buyer, and I\u2019d rather be upfront and price it fairly than oversell it. If you want something budget-friendly with potential, come have a look.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong-running powertrain, responsive transmission, and a chassis that still feels planted on the road. Not a showpiece, but it has the kind of honest mechanical character enthusiasts look for: starts up, moves out well, and offers a great foundation for a budget build, daily tinkering, or weekend revival. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, yet the car retains good bones and plenty of usable life for the next owner willing to give it some attention. Hard to find at this price point with this much potential.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_8",
